        Parameters:

        Throws:
        DkimException - If either the version, key type or service type given in the tags is incompatible to this library ('DKIM1', 'RSA' or 'Ed25519' and 'email' respectively).

        public void check​(String identity,
                  PrivateKey privateKey)
           throws DkimSigningException
        Checks, whether this DomainKey fits to the given identity and RSAPrivateKey.
        Parameters:
        identity - The identity.
        privateKey - The RSAPrivateKey.
        Throws:
        DkimSigningException - If either the granularity of this DomainKey doesn't match the given identity or the public key of this DomainKey doesn't belong to the given RSAPrivateKey.
